<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٣٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5889">‌مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ كَثِيرٍ، </a>أَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">‌سُفْيَانُ، </a>ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2043">‌أَبُو يَحْيَى الْقَتَّاتُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5410">‌مُجَاهِدٍ </a>قَالَ: «كُنْتُ مَعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">‌ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a>فَثَوَّبَ رَجُلٌ فِي الظُّهْرِ أَوِ الْعَصْرِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢١٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> اخْرُجْ بِنَا فَإِنَّ هَذِهِ بِدْعَةٌ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>